suites.command: rch exec -- cargo test -p fnp-conformance dtype_packet002_f_suites_are_green -- --nocapture
notes: Executes packet-002 dtype differential + metamorphic + adversarial lanes with deterministic seeds.
Differential mismatch artifact is emitted at crates/fnp-conformance/fixtures/packet002_dtype/oracle_outputs/dtype_differential_report.json.

quality_gates.command: rch exec -- cargo run -p fnp-conformance --bin validate_phase2c_packet -- --packet-id FNP-P2C-002

notes: Differential mismatch payload is machine-readable and carries expected/actual reason-code fields plus minimal repro artifact links when mismatches occur.
Each packet-002 dtype fixture carries replay-required fields: fixture_id, seed, mode, env_fingerprint, artifact_refs, reason_code.
Packet-F output is cross-linked to packet-E unit/property evidence and workflow scenario corpus; packet-G remains responsible for e2e replay scripts.
